OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1777539989
OL,3,CCars listed in fresh witness search
OL,4,Cafter sexual assault near M1 services
OL,6,FThe vehicles were in the area of
OL,7,FBaines Lane between 6.20pm and 6.40pm
OL,8,Fon Saturday, where the assault took
OL,9,Fplace - and are appealing for the
OL,10,Foccupants to come forward.
OL,12,FThe incident happened on an access
OL,13,Froad for the M1 southbound services.
OL,15,FShe was reportedly pulled to the
OL,16,Fground and sexually assaulted. When
OL,17,Fshe began shouting for help, the man
OL,18,Fran off towards the southbound
OL,19,Fservices.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
